    <abstract>
      <t>   This document specifies a lightweight authentication
   mechanism (KeyID, anti-replay, algorithms, truncation, and
   keying) intended to be reused by multiple protocol profiles.
   Concrete profiles define where the authentication data is
   carried and the exact coverage rules for header fields.

